<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-18370] BulkLoader tool initializes schema unnecessarily via streaming - 4.0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18370</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17740&quot; title=&quot;BulkLoader tool initializes schema unnecessarily via streaming&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17740&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17740&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;BulkLoader&lt;/tt&gt; initializes the schema/system keyspace, which caused the issue in bulk loader tool. See more details in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17740&quot; title=&quot;BulkLoader tool initializes schema unnecessarily via streaming&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17740&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17740&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Please help fix the issue in 4.0 branch as well. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
